popup.message: The Leecode Editor Extension works with leecode.com, leetcode.cn, or codetop.cc. Make sure you're on your page.

options_desc.message: This plugin can quickly open the leetcode topic on the web page in the IDE.

options_editor_tip.message: Select the version of the plugin, the IDE needs to install the IDE through the toolbox, and install the plugin Leetcode Editor.

options_project_tip.message: Fill in the ProjectName of the IDE.
